This application is in charge to illustrate how to use CARDAMOM LoadBalancing 
service with CARDAMOM System Management, receiving from it the notification 
and management of load balanced replica crashes

Steps to perform before building the demo
=========================================

	1) Configure the three hosts used for the demo:
		. ./HostConf.sh
           during the scipt execution, you have to specify the name of three hosts used for the demo

	2) Build the application
		make all

	3) Run the demo
		cd run/
		start_demo.sh

During the demo execution, you have to start some scripts contained in the run/ 
directory in order to perform the killing operations requested in the demo.
